metadata.name: PROTOTYPE
metadata.description:
"PROTOTYPE" is the apex of the vortex of DANKNESS engineering üòÆ‚Äçüí®ü§åüèº‚ú®

this piece is an exploration into PIXEL GLITCH, a new genre combining glitch and pixel art to form something unique.

what *creates* a genre of art? well... it's simply culture. vybes. something cool that people get.

both glitch and pixel art are incredibly native art-forms to web3. this is an experiment in a new direction, combining 2 art forms i've dearly grown to love over the last 2 years.

this is also the very first mint in the PIXELGLITCH collection.
